  "title": "Cabling Technician | Class 3 | Mandai | 5 Days | 9755",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Cabling Technician</strong><br /><strong>Industry: Telecommunications Engineering</strong><br /><strong>Location: Mandai</strong><br /><strong>5 Days | Monday to Friday 8am - 5pm / 8.30am - 5.30pm</strong><br /><strong>Salary: $2500 - $3500</strong></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>NITEC (Electrical Engineering / Electrical Technology / Electronic / IT ) or work- related experience</li><li>Class 3 driving license is a must</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Install, repair, test & commission cable systems (voice / data / fibre optics)</li><li>Performs termination and testing of new cabling</li><li>Prepare / Install cable pathways & supports</li><li>Assist in the preparation of tools & materials used for daily work assignments</li><li>Troubleshoot cabling system issues & perform repairs & maintenance</li><li>Assist co-workers with installation & routine maintenance of structured cabling systems</li><li>Work closely with client to manage schedule operations of assigned duties</li></ul><p><br />Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
